ldberg">，乌比·戈德堡</a>表达了她对梵蒂冈城缺乏蜜蜂的担忧，并计划解决这个问题。</p><p><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/whoopi-goldberg-mocks-ted-cruz-ben-shapiro-barbie-criticism-3473733">乌比·戈德堡嘲笑特德·克鲁兹和本·夏皮罗对“芭比”的批评</a></p><p>The Oscar-winning actor recently paid a visit to the holy city where she not only met the Pope, but also attended a nearby conservation art exhibition called <em>Changes</em> , which included images of bees and beekeepers at work.</p><p> After learning that the Vatican isn&#39;t home to any bees, the 67-year old said: “The Vatican should have bees,” according to <a href="https://www.vaticannews.va/en/world/news/2023-10/pope-francis-meeting-whoopi-goldberg-interview-vatican.html"><em>Vatican News</em></a> . She raised the increasing endangerment of the insect, adding: “Having bees brings attention to the fact that bees are dying all around the planet.”</p><p> <a href="https://reginahealthcare.com/blog/2023/01/10/are-bees-heading-towards-extinction/#:~:text=International%20Union%20of%20Conservation%20says,to%20the%20pollination%20of%20plants." target="_blank" rel="noopener">The International Union for Conservation of Nature</a> currently lists 20 species of bee as endangered, and 11 as critically endangered globally. Not only are they a vital part of the food chain, but they are crucial to maintaining the economy, with <a href="https://friendsoftheearth.uk/nature/14-facts-you-need-know-about-bees#:~:text=Since%201900%2C%20the%20UK%20has,wild%20bee%20species%20face%20extinction." target="_blank" rel="noopener">Friends Of The Earth</a> reporting that “it would cost UK farmers £1.8billion a year to pollinate our crops.”</p><p> After reportedly waiting over a decade to meet the Pope in person, and then learning of the lack of bees in the Vatican, the actor said: “Maybe I should send the Pope some bees.” </p><figure id="attachment_3514849" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3514849" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3514849" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2.jpg" alt="乌比戈德堡" width="2000" height="1335" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2-696x465.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2-1392x929.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Whoopi-Goldberg-2-1068x713.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3514849" class="wp-caption-text"> Whoopi Goldberg on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. CREDIT: Photo by Paul R. Giunta/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> While in the Vatican, Goldberg teased on her Instagram story that she may have been on location for her upcoming <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a> sequel, <em>Sister Act 3</em> , for which the release date is still not confirmed.</p><p> She said: “Picture <em>Sister Act</em> and all the nuns standing here, waiting for the Pope to come out. Maybe that&#39;s going to happen in the new movie. You don&#39;t know. You never know, but we are in Rome, and I am in Vatican City. What could I be doing? Why could I be here? We&#39;ll find out.”</p><p> Elsewhere, <em>Broad Ideas</em> podcaster <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/rachel-bilson-responds-to-whoopi-goldberg-criticism-on-the-view-3510872">Rachel Bilson has responded to Goldberg&#39;s criticism</a> of her comments on a recent episode.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/whoopi-goldberg-bees-pope-vatican-3514801">Whoopi Goldberg wants to send the Pope some bees</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
